articles.title: Apple Vision Pro failed to sell out on launch day - Notebookcheck.net
articles.description: Despite expectations, Apple has failed to sell out of its Vision Pro on launch day. This is despite estimates of day 1 availability being limited to between 60,000 and 80,000 units.
